OL,3,CFormer astrophysicist who had leg
OL,4,Camputated after crash 'an inspiration'
OL,6,FA former astrophysicist who had a leg
OL,7,Famputated after a crash is the
OL,8,Finspiration behind new specialist
OL,9,Fsupport for those who have lost limbs.
OL,11,FDr Alison Broadbent had her right leg
OL,12,Famputated above the knee after she was
OL,13,Fknocked down by a van in Acadia Road,
OL,14,Fin Bishop Auckland.
OL,16,FThe 58-year-old underwent several
OL,17,Fother operations, including skin
OL,18,Fgrafts, and spent two months in
OL,19,Fhospital.
