OL,3,CFormer astrophysicist who had leg
OL,4,Camputated after crash 'an inspiration'
OL,6,FDuring her recovery, Dr Broadbent said
OL,7,Fshe found there was a lack of peer
OL,8,Fsupport for amputees in the region and
OL,9,Fhas now set up NE Amputee.
OL,11,FThe dedicated group, backed by health
OL,12,Fprofessionals, offers specialist
OL,13,Fsupport and advice to amputees and
OL,14,Ftheir families.
OL,16,F"Coming to terms with the collision
OL,17,Fand what it meant for my life going
OL,18,Fforward was difficult and there were
OL,19,Fmany emotional times," said Dr
OL,20,FBroadbent.
