OL,3,CFormer astrophysicist who had leg
OL,4,Camputated after crash 'an inspiration'
OL,6,F"Once I got to the position in my
OL,7,Frecovery that I could help others I
OL,8,Falways wanted to, and that's where the
OL,9,Fidea of NE Amputee came from.
OL,11,F"The one thing I did miss was being
OL,12,Fable to talk to others going through
OL,13,Fthe same uncertainty and challenges I
OL,14,Fwas and being able to support one
OL,15,Fanother.
OL,17,F"I'd hope others who find themselves
OL,18,Fin a similar situation to what I did
OL,19,Fdon't feel they have to go through it
OL,20,Fby themselves as there's support out
OL,21,Fthere which makes such a difference."
