OL,6,FThe group was set up with the support
OL,7,Fof injury lawyers Irwin Mitchell, who
OL,8,Frepresented Dr Broadbent after the
OL,9,Fcollision.
OL,11,FLaura Mcilduff, a lawyer at the firm,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Through our work we often see
OL,13,Fthe impact losing a limb can have on
OL,14,Fclients but also how with access to
OL,15,Fspecialist support and rehabilitation
OL,16,Fthey can regain more of their
OL,17,Findependence.
