OL,3,CFormer astrophysicist who had leg
OL,4,Camputated after crash 'an inspiration'
OL,6,F"By bringing together professionals
OL,7,Facross a range of disciplines we can
OL,8,Foffer specialist support specifically
OL,9,Fdesigned to meet the needs of members."
OL,11,FIrwin Mitchell also helped secure Dr
OL,12,FBroadbent a settlement to fund the
OL,13,Fspecialist lifetime therapy and
OL,14,Fsupport she requires because of her
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,FSince the crash in November 2018, she
OL,18,Fhas visited the Ritz for afternoon
OL,19,Ftea, surfed in the North Sea, and
OL,20,Ftraveled to Mauritius.
