OL,6,F"Alison continues to be a real
OL,7,Finspiration and her selflessness to
OL,8,Fnow help others facing similar issues
OL,9,Fas to what she did is amazing,"
OL,10,Fcontinued Ms Mcilduff.
OL,12,F"We're proud to support the
OL,13,Fcommunities in which we operate and
OL,14,Fhelping launch NE Amputee alongside
OL,15,FAlison felt a natural extension that
OL,16,Fthat."
OL,18,FThe group held its first meeting last
OL,19,Fmonth in Gateshead.
